{"tid":161166,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"單身漢申請公屋司法覆核 法官判詞都好涼薄","createTime":"2017-03-18T10:49:24.000Z","updateTime":"2017-03-19T05:01:05.000Z","uid":19552,"like":0,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"a890c064ce429e5aba22df3d388ffcb8540866c2","tid":161166,"uid":19552,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-18T10:49:24.000Z","msg":"法官於判詞指，新計分制目的是為了減少年輕人不必要地盡早申請公屋，及提升社會流動性較低的較年長人士的上樓機會，這是合理的社會目的，而機制明顯合理地與目的相連。至於新制會否過份苛刻地限制單身非長者公屋申請人的權利，法官指現實中有限資源總是存在激烈競爭，雖然很難不去同情那些生活條件較差的單身年輕人，但亦不能忽略每有一個人上樓，便代表有人被拒絕上樓，新制不算對任何公屋申請人特別苛刻。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"410467ca14b6318c2a4b2e39fff64d249fd9af54","tid":161166,"uid":19552,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-18T10:51:23.000Z","msg":"49歲=年輕人<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0ac03609cc776739473a86e0fe11ed0f525b8727","tid":161166,"uid":89608,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-18T10:51:43.000Z","msg":"班老人家, 活咁多年, 唔係一直有地方住架咩"},{"pid":"913a319244c2497dd019636d9b8cf015fef90e4f","tid":161166,"uid":36901,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-18T10:52:42.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7e33ab756f8260c3bd7d2f8494d292aa0a3c5606","tid":161166,"uid":19552,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-18T10:57:57.000Z","msg":"Why新移民年青力壯可以優先上樓<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/19.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f58085c80c6de52f4137a3806d05ef5e2f050250","tid":161166,"uid":53026,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-19T05:01:05.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>Why新移民年青力壯可以優先上樓<img src=\"/assets/face